    <JadeMethod name="getTrackedItemBOL" id="8ee2bc9f-3028-4815-9273-25e30c758e45">
        <source>getTrackedItemBOL():String;
/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
19 May 2014	cnwndl1	Initial creation	Par 34142
30 May  2025 navrv30 MTN 34789 MTN | Query by BOL option doesn't return results for BOL-generated invoices
