/*

Purpose: This method wil identify if the Invoice Status is equals to INVOICE_POSTED_REVERSE.


Return Value : true or false

Date		Who		Reason
18 Jan 2022 jlika1	TFS 51891 CPL - Reprint Posted Returned Invoice

*/


begin		
	return self.status = INVOICE_POSTED_REVERSE ;
end;</source>
